<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Actress Amanda Seyfried, 34, and her husband Thomas Sadoski have welcomed a baby boy.</p>

<p>The couple announced the birth of their second child on social media through War Child USA, an organization dedicated to protecting children during war, on Monday.</p>

<p>The couple are already parents to their three-year-old daughter Nina. </p>

<p>It's a boy! Actress Amanda Seyfried, 34, and her husband Thomas Sadoski have welcomed a baby boy the couple announced on social media Monday (Pictured in 2019)</p>

<p>'We are so happy to join with INARA to be the first to announce that our ambassadors Amanda Seyfried and Thomas Sadoski welcomed their second child into this world,' the War Child USA account shared.</p>

<p>Along with the post the group gave a first glimpse at the baby boy through a sweet photo of the infant cradled in his dads arms.  </p>

<p>'Since the birth of our daughter 3 years ago our commitment to the innocent children that are so brutally affected by conflict and war has been a driving force in our lives,' Amanda and Thomas said in a statement. </p>

<p>'With the birth of our son the work of INARA and War Child has become our North Star,' they continued. </p>

